    <text>
        <body>
            
            
            <div xml:id="The Passing of the Hours"> 
                <interpGrp type="character">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="free">free</interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="sad">sad</interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="love">love</interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="society">society</interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <p>The hours steal by with still, unasking lips—</p>
                <p> So lightly that I cannot hear their tread;</p>
                <p>And softly touch me with their finger-tips</p>
                <p> To find if I be dreaming, or be dead.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>And yet however still their flight may be,</p>
                <p> Their ceaseless going weights my heart with tears;</p>
                <p>These touches will have wrought deep scars on me—</p>
                <p> When the light hours have worn to heavy years.</p>
            </div>
            
